== 评价 ==
[[烂番茄|烂番茄]]的[[评论聚合器|评论聚合器]]基于36条接受调查的评论，打出高達98%的“新鲜度”，给予本片积极评价，平均评价为7.7/10。网站共识写道：“强有力的自导自演作品，《迷失1971》保持忠于改编自真实事件的根源，剩下的就是扎扎实实地制作动作惊悚片<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/71_2015/|title='71  (2015)|work=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]]|accessdate=December 21, 2014|archive-date=2021-03-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210320070131/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/71_2015|dead-url=no}}</ref> 。”[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]则给出79/100的基于10条评论的评价<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/71|title='71|work=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]|accessdate=December 21, 2014|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112043050/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/71|dead-url=no}}</ref>
。

本片赢得[[英国独立电影奖|2014年英国独立电影奖]]的最佳导演奖<ref>{{cite web|url=http://variety.com/2014/film/news/benedict-cumberbatch-keira-knightley-attend-british-independent-film-awards-live-blog-1201373211/|title=Matthew Warchus’ ‘Pride’ Wins Top Prize at British Independent Film Awards|last=Barraclough|first=Leo|work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]|date=December 7, 2014|accessdate=December 21, 2014|archive-date=2020-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111234842/https://variety.com/2014/film/news/benedict-cumberbatch-keira-knightley-attend-british-independent-film-awards-live-blog-1201373211/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，兼有九项提名<ref>{{cite web|url=http://variety.com/2014/film/news/amy-gustin-deena-wallace-to-head-british-independent-film-awards-1201371851/|title=Amy Gustin, Deena Wallace to Head British Independent Film Awards|last=Barraclough|first=Leo|work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]|date=December 5, 2014|accessdate=December 21, 2014|archive-date=2021-01-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210123022917/https://variety.com/2014/film/news/amy-gustin-deena-wallace-to-head-british-independent-film-awards-1201371851/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

